  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Commissioning of a serialized electronic device (smartphone).",
    "masterDataAvailableFor carries the full product card: GS1-native attributes",
    "plus product-level electronics extensions (deviceCategory, modelIdentifier,",
    "repairabilityIndex, softwareSupport, energyEfficiency, weeeCompliance,",
    "rohsCompliance, circularityPerformance, emissionsPerformance, operatorInformation).",
    "All of these describe the GTIN, identical for every unit of this SKU, so they",
    "live with the product master data, not in ilmd (which is for lot-specific data).",
    "No ilmd: the EPC is a serialized item and we have no batch-specific data to assert.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: oec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,euelec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/electronics/",
    "See: extensions/common/core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
